  "texts": [
    "Next, we query the graph with retrieval and ranking processes to provide additional, relevant toxic knowl-edge.",
    "Extensive experiments and detailed case studies across various datasets show that MetaTox significantly lowers the false positive rate while improving overall toxicity detection performance in OOD scenarios.",
    "In addition, under in-domain scenarios, we surprisingly find that small language models are more competent.",
    "This work was supported by Shanghai \"Science and Technology Innovation Action Plan\" Project under Grant No.23511100700 and National Natural Science Foundation of China under Grant 42375146.",
    "Our study still has several limitations."
